snippet.textDisplay:
Coke Studio, Thank You for this Beautiful Gift as i remembered being a child sitting beside my MOM watching The Great TINA SANI perform this on TV as my Mom is her biggest Fan.
Shafqat Sir did an amazing job but i thought how great it would've been if you guys have collaborated with Tina Sani for this piece.
So i must suggest that please consider NAYYARA NOOR & TINA SANI in your future collaborations as these artists are Legends and an institutes in 'emselves. Also i think new generation should be given a chance to Enjoy the talent of these Artists as we did in our childhood.
snippet.textOriginal:
Coke Studio, Thank You for this Beautiful Gift as i remembered being a child sitting beside my MOM watching The Great TINA SANI perform this on TV as my Mom is her biggest Fan.
